## Usage

### Install

```sh
# yarn
yarn add -D eslint-plugin-sonar

# npm
npm install -D eslint-plugin-sonar
```

### Enable rules manually

```jsonc
// .eslintrc
{
  "plugins": ["sonar"],
  "rules": {
    "sonar/deprecation": 1
  }
}
```

### Extends configs

```jsonc
{
  "extends": [
    // only one of the following is needed to be enabled
    "plugin:sonar/base",
    "plugin:sonar/recommended"
  ]
}
```
